<html><head><title>Auto-fire for Archery now in-testing</title></head><body class="newsbody" ><div class=newbody><h2>EverQuest Vault -- EQ </h3><h3>Auto-fire for Archery now in-testing</h3><p>Ashlanne posted over on EQ Live that one of the most requested features ever for EQ is finally in testing - archery auto-fire.<br><br>Here's the full post:<blockquote>Greetings all,<br><br>I am pleased to announce that the designers and programmers have decided to implement auto-fire for archery.  This will be making its way to the Test Server in the next couple of days.  Once it is on the Test server please feel free to post here with your feedback, and to report any problems you find with the new ability.<br><br>Thanks all!</blockquote><br>This is great news.  Hopefully it's a feature everyone can take advantage of and not a high level AA ability.</div><p><div classs=copyright><font face=arial size=2 color=#959595>News Story from EverQuest Vault -- EQ <br>News Date: Wed 20 Oct 2004<br>Link: http://eqvault.ign.com//index.php#2673<br>Printed On: Fri Dec 17 3:29:03 PST 2004<br>©2004 IGN Entertainment</font></span>